크롤링 결과 5월 30일 부터 7월 4일 까지 총 29350개의 평점 data 를 얻을 수 있음

review_total <- read.xlsx('C:/Users/chongs/Desktop/git/R/R/R_Statics/R_Statics/bugs.xlsx', sheetName = 'Sheet1',encoding = 'UTF-8')
temp_date <-review_total$time
temp_date <- strptime(temp_date, '%Y.%m.%d')

review_total$date <- as.character(temp_date)
review_total$hour <- as.character(strptime(review_total$time, "%Y.%m.%d %H"))
review_total$score <- as.numeric(as.character(review_total$score))
review_total <- filter(review_total, date !='2019-07-05')

Word cloud

word <- data.frame(lapply(review_total$review, as.character), stringsAsFactors=FALSE)
word[] <- lapply(review_total$review,as.character)



a <- sapply(word,extractNoun,USE.NAMES=F)
a <- unlist(a)           
a <- str_replace_all(a,"/^[a-zA-Z]+$/",'')            #영어 삭제
a <- str_replace_all(a,"[^/가-힣/]",'')            #한글 제외 삭제
a <- str_replace_all(a," ",'')  
a <- Filter(function(x){nchar(x)<=6 & nchar(x)>=2},a)
a <- gsub('영화','',a)
a <- gsub('하게','',a)
a <- gsub('게','',a)
a <- gsub('근데','',a)
a <- gsub('기','',a)
a <- gsub('해서','',a)
wordcount <- table(a)
palete <- brewer.pal(11,'Spectral')
wordcloud(names(wordcount),freq=wordcount,scale=c(5,1),rot.per=0.25, min.freq=50,
          random.order=F,random.color=T,colors=palete)

계층, 충격, 냄새, 반지하, 찜찜, 가난, 빈부격차, 바퀴벌레 등 영화의 핵심을 표현하는 단어들이 주로 나타남.


Daily 기준으로 전처리를 진행 : 평점 평균 데이터, 평점 갯수 데이터

mean_score <- review_total %>%
  group_by(date) %>%
  summarise(mean_score = mean(score, na.rm = T), sd_score = sd(score))


count_review <- review_total %>%
  group_by(date) %>%
  tally()
options(scipen=100)

#일별 평점 갯수 추이
count_score_plot <- ggplot(data=count_review,aes(x=date, y=n,group=1))+
  geom_line(color = 'red')+
  ggtitle('일별 평점 갯수 추이')+
  theme(panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
        panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
        axis.text.x = element_text(angle=45, hjust=1, vjust=1),
        plot.title = element_text(face = 'bold', size = 15, vjust=2))



#일별 평점 평균 추이

데이터 전처리

# 시간에 따른 평균 평점 data set
mean_score_hour <- review_total %>%
  group_by(hour) %>%
  summarise(mean_score = mean(score, na.rm = T), sd_score = sd(score))

#week로 자르기
mean_score_hour$week <- week(mean_score_hour$hour)
mean_score_week_23 <- mean_score_hour %>%
  filter(week == 23)


#day 로자르기
mean_score_hour$date<- date(mean_score_hour$hour)
mean_score_day6_3 <- mean_score_hour %>%
  filter(date == '2019-06-03')


#시간별 평점 갯수

count_score_hour <- review_total %>%
  group_by(hour) %>%
  tally()

#week로 자르기
count_score_hour$week <- week(count_score_hour$hour)
count_score_week_23 <- count_score_hour %>%
  filter(week == 23)


#day 로자르기
count_score_hour$date<- date(count_score_hour$hour)
count_score_day6_3 <- count_score_hour %>%
  filter(date == '2019-06-03')
